<template>
    <ProductsGridItem :product="product" :v-for="product in products"/>
</template>

<script>
import ProductsGridItem from '../components/ProductsGridItem.vue';
export default {
    name: 'ProductsGrid',
    props: {
        products: {
            type: Array,
            required: true
        }
    },
    components: {
        ProductsGridItem
    }
}
</script>
